high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink counter.
Pick up the green and yellow dishsponge from behind the bottle.
Turn around, turn left, enter the bedroom, turn right and go to the pan.
Put the dishsponge in the pan on the bed.
Pick up the pan with the sponge in it.
Turn right to the white cabinet.
Put the pan with the sponge in it on the bottom shelf of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put DishSponge in Pan on the bottom shelf of the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the back of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the dishsponge from the right side of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward then left into the pan.
Put the dishsponge into the pan on the bed.
Pick up the pan with the sponge in it.
Turn around towards the tall white cabinet.
Put the pan with sponge in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the DishSponge and Pan in the Cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the dish sponge, right to the dish washing liquid, from the sink.
Turn back and walk towards the sofa, then turn left and enter into the bedroom, turn right and walk, turn left towards the bed.
Put the dish sponge into the pan, right back to the spatula, on the bed.
Pick up the pan with sponge in it from the bed.
Turn left beside to the cabinet.
Put the pan with dish sponge in it on the last rack of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with dish sponge in it, on the bedroom cabinet.
